#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.138"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.138:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.138:0.2"
msgid "14. Puggalavagga "
msgstr "14. Persons "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: nikaṭṭhapuggalasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.138:0.3"
msgid "138. Nikaṭṭhasutta "
msgstr "138. Retreat "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.138:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, these four people are found in the world. "

msgctxt "an4.138:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

#. HTML: </p><ol>
msgctxt "an4.138:1.3"
msgid "Nikaṭṭhakāyo anikaṭṭhacitto, anikaṭṭhakāyo nikaṭṭhacitto, anikaṭṭhakāyo ca anikaṭṭhacitto ca, nikaṭṭhakāyo ca nikaṭṭhacitto ca. "
msgstr "~One is on retreat in body, but not mind; ~one is on retreat in mind, but not body; ~one is on retreat in neither body nor mind; and ~one is on retreat in both body and mind. "

#. HTML: </ol><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.138:2.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo nikaṭṭhakāyo hoti anikaṭṭhacitto? "
msgstr "And how is a person on retreat in body, but not mind? "

#. VAR: araññavanapatthāni → araññe vanapatthāni (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "an4.138:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevati. "
msgstr "It’s when a person frequents remote lodgings in the wilderness and the forest. "

msgctxt "an4.138:2.3"
msgid "So tattha kāmavitakkampi vitakketi byāpādavitakkampi vitakketi vihiṃsāvitakkampi vitakketi. "
msgstr "But they think sensual, malicious, and cruel thoughts. "

msgctxt "an4.138:2.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo nikaṭṭhakāyo hoti anikaṭṭhacitto. "
msgstr "That’s how a person is on retreat in body, but not mind. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.138:3.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo anikaṭṭhakāyo hoti nikaṭṭhacitto? "
msgstr "And how is a person on retreat in mind, but not body? "

msgctxt "an4.138:3.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo naheva kho araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevati. "
msgstr "It’s when a person doesn’t frequent remote lodgings in the wilderness and the forest. "

msgctxt "an4.138:3.3"
msgid "So tattha nekkhammavitakkampi vitakketi abyāpādavitakkampi vitakketi avihiṃsāvitakkampi vitakketi. "
msgstr "But they think thoughts of renunciation, good will, and harmlessness. "

msgctxt "an4.138:3.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo anikaṭṭhakāyo hoti nikaṭṭhacitto. "
msgstr "That’s how a person is on retreat in mind, but not body. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.138, sc4
msgctxt "an4.138:4.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo anikaṭṭhakāyo ca hoti anikaṭṭhacitto ca? "
msgstr "And how is a person on retreat in neither body nor mind? "

msgctxt "an4.138:4.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo naheva kho araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevati. "
msgstr "It’s when a person doesn’t frequent remote lodgings in the wilderness and the forest. "

msgctxt "an4.138:4.3"
msgid "So tattha kāmavitakkampi vitakketi byāpādavitakkampi vitakketi vihiṃsāvitakkampi vitakketi. "
msgstr "And they think sensual, malicious, and cruel thoughts. "

msgctxt "an4.138:4.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo anikaṭṭhakāyo ca hoti anikaṭṭhacitto ca. "
msgstr "That’s how a person is on retreat in neither body nor mind. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an4.138:5.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo nikaṭṭhakāyo ca hoti nikaṭṭhacitto ca? "
msgstr "And how is a person on retreat in both body and mind? "

msgctxt "an4.138:5.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo araññavanapatthāni pantāni senāsanāni paṭisevati. "
msgstr "It’s when a person frequents remote lodgings in the wilderness and the forest. "

msgctxt "an4.138:5.3"
msgid "So tattha nekkhammavitakkampi vitakketi abyāpādavitakkampi vitakketi avihiṃsāvitakkampi vitakketi. "
msgstr "And they think thoughts of renunciation, good will, and harmlessness. "

msgctxt "an4.138:5.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo nikaṭṭhakāyo ca hoti nikaṭṭhacitto ca. "
msgstr "That’s how a person is on retreat in both body and mind. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.138:5.5"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmin”ti. "
msgstr "These are the four people found in the world.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.138:5.6"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
